Class Intercambio_Masa

java.lang.Object
co.com.mycompany.methods.Intercambio_Masa
public class Intercambio_Masa extends Object
The Intercambio_Masa class is used for converting mass measurements and includes methods for setting and getting the conversion factors and mass value.
